== Setup
  1. bash < <( curl http://rvm.beginrescueend.com/releases/rvm-install-head )
  2. add the following entry into .bashrc file
    if [[ -s "$HOME/.rvm/scripts/rvm" ]]  ; then source "$HOME/.rvm/scripts/rvm" ; fi
  3. rvm install 1.9.2
  4. rvm 1.9.2
  5. sudo apt-get install sqlite3 libsqlite3-dev
  6. sudo gem install sqlite3-ruby
